{"tid":2382550,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"優秀關員認家中藏弩及鋼棒 稱只為收藏與示威無關 鄭念慈表明打算判監","createTime":"2021-01-27T10:44:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T13:56:33.000Z","uid":56115,"like":4,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2a2e94b2d6090f611c91bd356aee5f91c47f962a","tid":2382550,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T10:44:24.000Z","msg":"曾獲海關嘉許及表明可獲特快晉升的關員，去年7月被警方在其住所內搜出弩及彈簧鋼棒，警誡下承認管有涉案物品。關員今在九龍城裁判法院承認無牌管有槍械及違禁武器兩罪，求情指<span class=\"red\">有關物品只是放在家中收藏，與示威無關</span>。裁判官鄭念慈表明打算判監，押後案件至下月11日，待索閱被告的背景及社會服務令報告後始判刑，其間被告還柙。<br />\n<br />\n鄭官亦特別向被告指出，別以為報告建議他接受社會服務令，法庭便會依照報告建議判刑。"},{"pid":"2c5e86130d87abb61b74716cf331bae383e68540","tid":2382550,"uid":56115,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T10:44:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210127/YEPW4QEETNHGVGOWSK3Q4POR2I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210127%2FYEPW4QEETNHGVGOWSK3Q4POR2I%2F&d=vmCIlZEHEchodQF1AoZdn%2Bbr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=319e0eac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210127%2FYEPW4QEETNHGVGOWSK3Q4POR2I%2F&h=85212ab5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210127/YEPW4QEETNHGVGOWSK3Q4POR2I/</a>"},{"pid":"c00f1e31eb3c0207a349fb58624ee5997850d77d","tid":2382550,"uid":231480,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T10:45:56.000Z","msg":"粒大癦，化咗灰都認得佢"},{"pid":"d7c24ac758307f08e51e80da6ccd6f547ade76b8","tid":2382550,"uid":271516,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T10:49:07.000Z","msg":"幾時拉哂賣wargame野果班？"},{"pid":"44432b26287357bed29cde90dbb3dc8c5fce8a60","tid":2382550,"uid":35783,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T10:49:35.000Z","msg":"個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以為女人黎"},{"pid":"636ae369e3fa63cf49b8ef759c364093d666e4e0","tid":2382550,"uid":231480,"like":5,